		<abstract id="abstract">
			<title>Background processing in Eclipse Plug-ins</title>
			<para> This tutorial describes how to do asynchronous work within
				Eclipse plug-ins and RCP applications.
				It explains the usage of
				the
				Jobs API
				for
				performing
				asynchronous
				tasks.
			</para>
			<para>This
				tutorial can be used for Eclipse 3.x and Eclipse 4.x based
				plug-ins.
			</para>
		</abstract>
